FFMpeg install instructions
----------------------------

Windows
-------
Follow the instructions here for windows
http://www.wowzamedia.com/forums/content.php?213-FFmpeg-with-Wowza-Server-(MPEG-TS)

Linux
-----
As root
# yum install ffmpeg ffmpeg-devel

FFMPEG Command
-------------
The command to run ffmpeg is 
ffmpeg -i <input file> -re -ar 22050 -vcodec libx264 -vpre default -f flv rtmp://localhost/<application_name>/<akamai_ingress_stream_name>

Note: the default application_name is akamaiTest and the 
default akamai_ingress_stream_name is testStream43841

